data.description: If you are looking for a quiet spot on a small fishing lake, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1352 sq.ft. 2000 year old mfg.home would fit the bill. Home also has a 4'crawl with a bilco door. 20'x20'older barn w/lean to. Stoned storm shelter built in bank. Home fronts Cortright Lake which also has outlet to Cortright Lake 11(over 15 acres of fishing)
